Package: alot
Architecture: any
Homepage: https://github.com/pazz/alot
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-magic (>=5.04), python-configobj (>=4.6.0), python-twisted (>=10.2.0), python-notmuch (>= 0.12), python-urwid (>= 1.0)
Description: Terminal MUA using notmuch mail
  Alot is a terminal-based mail user agent for the notmuch mail system.
  It features a modular and command prompt driven interface to provide
  a full MUA experience as an alternative to the Emacs mode shipped
  with notmuch.
